pl.edu.icm.cermine.service

Interface CermineExtractorService

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    CermineExtractorServiceImpl

    public interface CermineExtractorService
    Abstraction of the service used to extract metadata from submitted files. Service is responsible for extraction and proper scheduling and resource allocation.
    Author:
    Aleksander Nowinski (a.nowinski@icm.edu.pl)
